Title: 169: Data Science: Technology and Philanthropy
Description:
In this episode of the SuperDataScience Podcast, I chat with the CEO, Founder and AI Neuroscience Researcher, Tarry Singh. You will hear about the three essential components of businesses, learn the 5 main steps to excel in Deep Learning, and hear how Machine Learning, Artificial Intelligence and Deep Learning could drastically change the economic status of third-world countries.
